AirPods are the Company's wireless headphones that interact with Siri. Apple Watch is the Company's line of smart watches. api_list.name: get-meta-data
api_list.description: Get meta data that supports for other endpoints
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cnbc.p.rapidapi.com/get-meta-data"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cnbc.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
